{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/editor-komik-idaman-versi-author-ciayo-comics/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Editor Komik Idaman Versi Author CIAYO Comics","content":"\n<p>Dalam sebuah komik, peran editor sangat penting. Tugas editor adalah memeriksa seluruh aspek komik sebelum diterbitkan, mulai dari cerita, paneling, hasil akhir, dan masih banyak lagi. Tugas editor bukan hanya mengoreksi komik, tetapi mengarahkan komik agar solid dari berbagai macam aspek. Ini adalah kunci utama menjadi editor komik idaman para author.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mungkin kamu penasaran, seperti apa sih sosok editor yang baik itu? Karena pekerjaan editor banyak tersembunyi di balik layar, sayangnya tidak banyak yang tahu seperti apa pekerjaan editor dan bagaimana mereka berkolaborasi dengan author komik. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"44613\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/meriahnya-comic-frontier-x-bersama-ciayo-comics/attachment/05-comic-frontier-x/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-comic-frontier-x.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-comic-frontier-x\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-comic-frontier-x-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-comic-frontier-x.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-comic-frontier-x.jpg\" alt=\"Untuk jadi editor komik idaman, seorang editor harus bisa berkolaborasi dengan komikusnya. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-44613\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-comic-frontier-x.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-comic-frontier-x-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Untuk jadi editor komik idaman, seorang editor harus bisa berkolaborasi dengan komikusnya. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk menjawab pertanyaan tersebut, CIAYO Blog ketemu sama\nbeberapa author komik CIAYO Comics. Pertanyaan yang diajukan ke mereka sangat\nsederhana: Seperti apa sih editor komik yang baik itu? Sebagai author yang\nsudah lama bekerja dengan editor mereka, tentunya cerita dari para author komik\nCIAYO Comics bakalan menarik dan juga bermanfaat. Siapa tahu kamu juga bisa\nmengambil banyak pesan moral dari cerita mereka!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tanpa basa-basi lagi, langsung saja disimak kriteria editor komik idaman versi author komik CIAYO Comics!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tips-dan-langkah-membuat-komik-one-shot-dalam-format-webtoon/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tips Membuat Komik One Shot Dalam Format Webtoon</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Editor Komik idaman Menurut Author Komik CIAYO Comics</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Johanes Park (<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/wonder-sweet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Wonder Sweet (opens in a new tab)\">Wonder Sweet</a>)</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"51076\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/gula-comic-pesan-berwarna-wonder-sweet/attachment/04-gula-comic/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-gula-comic.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-gula-comic\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-gula-comic-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-gula-comic.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-gula-comic.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Gula Comic\" class=\"wp-image-51076\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-gula-comic.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-gula-comic-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: Gula Comic</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Editor komik yang baik itu netral, terbuka pikirannya, mempunyai\nbanyak referensi dan tidak bias terhadap selera dan ambisi sendiri, huhu…</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>FairyDemon (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Rika si Preman Sekolah (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/rika-si-preman-sekolah\" target=\"_blank\">Rika si Preman Sekolah</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/pinkmosphere\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Pinkmosphere (opens in a new tab)\">Pinkmosphere</a>)</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53695\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pinkmosphere-saat-adiknya-rika-si-preman-sekolah-jatuh-cinta/attachment/05-pinkmosphere/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-pinkmosphere\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere.jpg\" alt=\"Kakaknya Edo ganti dari Rika jadi Suzakura, hehe. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53695\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-pinkmosphere-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Editor komik yang baik itu editor yang lebih condong ke membimbing:\nmembantu nunjukin kesalahan komikusnya dan ngasih tahu apa yang sebaiknya diperbaiki,\nketimbang editor yang nyuruh rombak konsep komiknya dan ujung-ujungnya malah\njauh dari kehendak komikusnya. Beda cerita kalo konsepnya udah ditolak dari\nawal karena ngaco, itu salah komikusnya berarti.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Fei Rizani (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Imaginarium (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/imaginarium\" target=\"_blank\">Imaginarium</a>)</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54188\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/editor-komik-idaman-versi-author-ciayo-comics/attachment/01-editor-idaman/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-editor-idaman.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-editor-idaman\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-editor-idaman-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-editor-idaman.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-editor-idaman.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54188\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-editor-idaman.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-editor-idaman-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Editorkomik idaman itu yang mengerti isi, maksud, dan tujuan\nkarya anaknya dan mau mengarahkan ke arah sana. Bisa melihat kekurangan dan\nkelebihan anaknya dan menyesuaikan editorial dengan mindset itu. Keep the\nauthor in track dan ngingetin kalau suatu saat si author keluar dari jalur dan\ntujuannya. Punya balance yang baik antara pemenuhan keinginan pasar dan\nidealisme author. Intinya menambal yang kurang dan mengasah yang lebih biar\nmakin tajamzzz…</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Snow Rexilium (<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/jakarta-titik-nol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Jakarta Titik Nol (opens in a new tab)\">Jakarta Titik Nol</a>)</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54092\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/attachment/04-jakarta-titik-nol/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-jakarta-titik-nol\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" alt=\"Keegoisan manusia akan menjadi senjata makan tuan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54092\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Yang ngebimbing, nggak maksain untuk ngeubah cerita sesuai\nseleranya (dalam artian mungkin sampe kek ambil alih, &#8220;Eh yg bikin cerita\ngw apa elu?&#8221;), tetapi ngasih masukan dan mengarahkan secara konstrutif\nsampai tahap decision. Bisa diajak diskusi dan nggak mengintimidasi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Mas Hiro (<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/linked-soul\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Linked Soul (opens in a new tab)\">Linked Soul</a>)</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54189\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/editor-komik-idaman-versi-author-ciayo-comics/attachment/02-editor-idaman/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-editor-idaman.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-editor-idaman\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-editor-idaman-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-editor-idaman.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-editor-idaman.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54189\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-editor-idaman.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-editor-idaman-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Mampu memberi jalan tengah antara ideologi platform dan\nidealisme komikus. Memberi motivasi, dorongan mental, serta nasehat tentang bagaimana\nmenghadapi permasalahan-permasalahan di dunia profesional (termasuk cara\nmenyikapi komentar pembaca, sikap di sosmed, cara baca kontrak, HAKI, dll)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Dini Marlina (<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/blue-serenade\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Blue Serenade (opens in a new tab)\">Blue Serenade</a>)</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"42388\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/blue-serenade-komik-romance-terbaru/attachment/2-2-32/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;SMPN 170&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1516273913&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber : CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber : CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-5.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-5.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber : CIAYO Comics)\" class=\"wp-image-42388\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sumber : CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Yang beneran kasih saran dan masukan dengan cara yang baik.\nJadi harus netral, bisa ambil titik tengah dari banyak ide entah dari\nkomikus/penulis. Jangan egois sama pendapat pribadi (duh jadi inget yg dulu.\nhaha). Yang jelas sih bisa ngarahin alur ceritanya supaya lebih menarik.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Itu dia gambaran editor komik idaman versi author komik CIAYO Comics. Mudah-mudahan bisa memberikan gambaran seperti apa tugas para editor komik, ya. Dan buat kamu yang pingin ngomik di CIAYO Comics, nggak usah takut ketemu editor-editor yang galak dan ngeselin. Tim editorial CIAYO Comics asik banget buat diajak kerja bareng dan pastinya profesional serta tahu segala ilmu dan teknik untuk bikin komik kamu makin oke. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Penasaran gimana caranya submit komik ke CIAYO Comics? <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cara-submisi-komik-ciayo-comics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Klik link ini (opens in a new tab)\">Klik link ini</a> untuk cari tahu tata caranya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4bd7bfbb-cbf9-54b9-9ab1-1c53fa34fd11"}}}